Grounded heard the message than hearing Nightlight choosing to leave, 
decides to join the group.  "This meeting is adjurned.  Sarge and 
Aerotaur will train Trinity beggining by the first heat of the sun 
tommorrow."  turning he walked out of the room then ran for the door. 
"Nightlight" he said through comm link" i will join, through the tremor 
his ship amde I have pinpointed his location to this spot.  (transfers 
location.)  "  Grounded then jumped transforming onto a mole and diving 
into hte ground burrowing at amazing speed.
